These OpenGL wrappers for Gwydion Dylan are copyright (C) by 
Jefferson Dubrule.  Redistribution is granted under a modified GNU
Library General Public License.

The modification is that a work that links to this library is no
longer required to be able to link to a modified version of the
library.  Because of a lack of robustness in preserving binary
compatibility in current versions of d2c, this is simply not possible.

